name: Not Enough Space (Justin Ignatowski, dje417, mchrpt, BenjaminOSlattery)
name_original: Not Enough Space (Justin Ignatowski, dje417, mchrpt, BenjaminOSlattery)
description:
A competive game about self-preservation on an asteroid hurtling through space
Made for WPI JamFest 2023 (Prisoner's Dilemma)

Move - A/D
Use - R
Swap Building - Q/E/Scroll
Place - Right Mouse Button
Cancel - Left Mouse Button
